Package org.apache.jackrabbit.commons.flat

Interface TreeTraverser.ErrorHandler

  • Enclosing class:
    TreeTraverser
    public static interface TreeTraverser.ErrorHandler
    Error handler for handling RepositoryExceptions occurring on traversal. The predefined IGNORE error handler can be used to ignore all exceptions.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static TreeTraverser.ErrorHandler IGNORE
      Predefined error handler which ignores all exceptions.
